          "briefTitle": "Open Suction Circuit Flushing With Chlorhexidine Decreases Ventilator-Associated Pneumonia: A Quasi-experimental Study",
          "officialTitle": "The Effect of Suction System Flushing With Chlorhexidine on the Occurrence of Ventilator-Associated Pneumonia Among Mechanically Ventilated Patients"
        },
